---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';

const title = 'Art & Crafts Fulfillment | Material-Specific Packaging, Humidity Control, Premium Gift Wrapping | MTP';
const description = 'Specialized fulfillment for art supplies, craft materials, paints, canvas, beads, paper. Material-specific packaging, humidity 40-60%, temperature 10-25°C, gift wrapping option, 99.8% accuracy, 100% insurance, 24-48 hour delivery.';
const ogImage = 'https://profm.ua/images/fulfillment-crafts.jpg';

const schema = {
  '@context': 'https://schema.org',
  '@type': 'Service',
  name: title,
  description: description,
  provider: {
    '@type': 'Organization',
    name: 'MTP Group',
    url: 'https://profm.ua/en/'
  },
  areaServed: {
    '@type': 'Country',
    name: 'UA'
  },
  priceRange: '₴60-₴150'
};
---

<Base title={title} description={description} ogImage={ogImage} lang="en">
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-red-600 to-red-500 text-white py-16 sm:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold mb-6 leading-tight">
        Art &amp; Crafts Fulfillment<br />Specialized Packaging, Climate Control, Premium Gift Wrapping
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl mb-8 opacity-95 leading-relaxed">
        Art supplies, paints, canvas, paper, beads, craft materials. Material-specific packaging, humidity 40-60%, temperature 10-25°C, premium gift wrapping option, 99.8% accuracy, 100% insurance, 24-48 hour delivery.
      </p>
      <a href="#contact" class="inline-block bg-white text-red-600 px-8 py-4 rounded font-bold text-lg hover:bg-gray-100 transition">
        Start Art & Crafts Fulfillment
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Why Art & Crafts Materials Need Specialized Fulfillment</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">🎨 Extreme Product Diversity</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Thin art paper to heavy paint jars. Tiny seed beads to large canvases. Each product type requires different handling. Requires flexible, specialized packing system.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">💧 Humidity &amp; Temperature Sensitivity</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Paper warps at humidity &gt;70%. Paint hardens or thins with temperature changes. Requires strict 40-60% humidity and 10-25°C temperature control.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">🎁 Gift Purchase Context</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Craft materials often purchased as gifts. Premium presentation matters. Unboxing experience influences gift satisfaction. Presentation = part of the product value.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">📦 Bulk &amp; Volume Challenge</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Craft supplies lightweight but bulky—0.5kg can occupy 30×30×15cm. Requires volume optimization for space efficiency without sacrificing protection.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

\1  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">How MTP Group Handles Art & Craft Supply Orders</h2>
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none mb-12">
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
          With 10 years of experience in specialized fulfillment and over 150 active clients, MTP Group has optimized every step of order processing. Our 3,900 m² warehouse is purpose-built for high-velocity fulfillment across diverse categories.
        </p>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">The Fulfillment Challenge</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
          Art supply retailers face a unique challenge: inventory includes everything from delicate canvas and paper to fragile paints and ceramics. Orders often contain 5–15 different items, each requiring specific handling to prevent damage.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
          MTP Group's approach: Our warehouse zones separate fragile materials from bulk items. Paint jars are stored vertically in secure compartments. Canvas and paper are on specialized shelving. When an order arrives, staff navigate climate-controlled zones sequentially—paint section, paper section, beads/supplies section. This structured workflow delivers picking times of 3–5 minutes while maintaining zero breakage rates.
        </p>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Why Retailers Choose MTP</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          Art supply margins vary: canvas 25–30%, paints 20–25%, craft materials 35–40%. Broken goods and returns eliminate margins entirely. Our <strong>99.8% picking accuracy</strong> with damage-free packing means zero loss orders.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          MTP Group has processed <strong>12,000+ craft supply orders processed, 35+ art retailers served</strong>. Our experience in this category translates to faster integration, fewer picking errors, and predictable costs.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

   Art & Crafts Services</h2>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">✓ Climate Control by Material Type</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Paper stored at 40-60% humidity. Paints at 10-25°C stable temperature. Textiles protected from light. Each material type in optimal microclimate.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">✓ Material-Specific Packaging</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Paper on space-efficient platforms. Paint jars in sealed containers. Beads in protective compartments. Canvas on roll tubes. Custom packaging per item type.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">✓ Quality Verification &amp; Integrity Check</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Each item inspected for integrity, completeness, specification match. 99.8% picking accuracy. Batch dates verified. Damage detected before shipment.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">✓ Premium Gift Wrapping Option</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Customers can select gift wrapping at checkout. Beautiful packaging with ribbon and presentation. Craft materials arrive gift-ready with zero additional effort.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Pricing for Art & Crafts</h2>
      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border border-gray-200 mb-8">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-4">Fulfillment &amp; Packaging</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
          <li class="flex justify-between">
            <span>Picking per order</span>
            <span class="font-bold">15–25 UAH</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex justify-between">
            <span>Material-specific packing</span>
            <span class="font-bold">5–15 UAH</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex justify-between">
            <span>Premium gift wrapping (optional)</span>
            <span class="font-bold">20–50 UAH</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex justify-between">
            <span>Climate control included</span>
            <span class="font-bold">Included</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex justify-between">
            <span>Standard delivery</span>
            <span class="font-bold">40–100 UAH</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex justify-between">
            <span>100% insurance coverage</span>
            <span class="font-bold">Included</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-red-50 p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
        <h3 class="font-bold mb-3">Example: Art Supply Retailer (300 orders/month)</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          Picking &amp; packing: 300 × (20 + 10) = 9,000 UAH<br/>
          Delivery: 300 × 70 = 21,000 UAH<br/>
          Climate-controlled storage (2 pallets): 2 × 300 = 600 UAH/month<br/>
          <strong class="text-lg">TOTAL: 30,600 UAH/month = 102 UAH per order</strong><br/>
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-600">Includes: material-specific packing, 40-60% humidity, 10-25°C temperature, climate control, 99.8% accuracy, 100% insurance</span>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Quality &amp; Material Preservation Guarantees</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="text-center bg-white p-6 rounded border border-green-200">
          <p class="text-4xl font-bold text-green-600 mb-2">99.8%</p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 font-bold">Picking Accuracy</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-2">Every item verified</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center bg-white p-6 rounded border border-green-200">
          <p class="text-4xl font-bold text-green-600 mb-2">40–60%</p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 font-bold">Humidity Control</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-2">Paper & material preservation</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center bg-white p-6 rounded border border-green-200">
          <p class="text-4xl font-bold text-green-600 mb-2">Premium</p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 font-bold">Gift Presentation</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-2">Wrap-ready delivery option</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Why Fulfillment Speed & Accuracy Matter for Your Business</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">⏱️ Speed = Competitive Advantage</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">E-commerce customers expect 24-48 hour delivery. Slow fulfillment leads to lost orders and negative reviews. MTP Group's 2-4 hour order processing means your customers receive tracking updates the same day they order. This builds trust and encourages repeat purchases. Faster fulfillment also reduces storage costs by turning inventory quickly.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">✅ Accuracy = Customer Retention</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Wrong item? The customer will return it, costing you both labor and shipping. Wrong quantity? Dispute and potential chargeback. Our 99.95%+ accuracy means customers receive exactly what they ordered—building satisfaction and driving 30-40% repeat order rates. Happy customers become your marketing channel through word-of-mouth and reviews.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">💰 Margins Are Everything</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Fulfillment is often 10-20% of your total order cost. Partner with a provider who understands your margin structure and helps you optimize every step. MTP Group's transparent pricing and category expertise mean you pay only for what you use, with no hidden fees. Our 10 years of experience has helped 150+ retailers identify cost-saving opportunities.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">🔄 Scaling Without Stress</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Black Friday. Holiday season. New product launch. These peak periods either make or break your year. You need a fulfillment partner who scales with you—not one that delays orders during your busiest time. MTP Group guarantees 2-3x capacity scaling on 7 days' notice, ensuring your customers always get on-time delivery even during peak volume.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-red-600 to-red-500 text-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Ready to Scale Your Art & Crafts Fulfillment?</h2>
      <p class="text-xl mb-8 opacity-90">
        Material-specific packaging, climate control (40-60% humidity), 99.8% accuracy, premium gift wrapping option, 24-48 hour delivery, 100% insurance. Start today.
      </p>
      <a href="#contact" class="inline-block bg-white text-red-600 px-8 py-4 rounded font-bold text-lg hover:bg-gray-100 transition">
        Request a Quote
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(schema)}></script>
</Base>
